This is a website based on RoR 3.1 to provide university(in China) associations create their own portal service.
It's consist of CMS and OA.
Road map: 1. News publish and static pages. 2. comments and theme support 3. albums and friend associations 4. activity and OA
Now step 1 is nearly finish.
Use gems list: ckeditor, authlogic, will_paginate
This is my first product, I hope can learn something from this project.


